          <actionDate>2017-02-06</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Locality-based Social Security Benefits Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Social Security Administration to increase an individual's monthly Old Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance benefit amount&nbsp;in&nbsp;accordance with the locality-based comparability payment rate applicable to the federal locality-pay area in which the individual resides.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
